## 💡 Pending Decisions

### Cart — Add to Cart Interaction
Two approaches under consideration:

**Option A — Size Popup on Add**
Show a popup that asks for size selection when user taps Add to Cart. Quantity defaults to 1. Cleaner intent but adds a step.

**Option B — Inline Quantity Bar**
Quantity bar appears in place of the Add to Cart button after first tap. Faster repeat adds but requires size to be pre-selected.

**Note:** Both options add friction on first add but can be bypassed via the Menu Card component directly.

