31st March, 2026
Animated Flatlist with reanimated was a mistake it gives a jittery effect when switching slides
once carousel reaches end or user tries to go backwards, felt unnatural and bugged.
Im switching to react-native-reanimated-carousel for out of the box infinite carousel 
support and better performance.

